<p>For example, instead of targeting &#8220;Italian restaurants,&#8221; businesses could use &#8220;family-friendly Italian restaurant in Boston.&#8221;</p>
<p>â€œThis hyper-personalization targets the <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/niche-markets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niche audience</a> directly and increases conversion probability,â€ added Gianluca Ferruggia, general manager of B2B marketplace <a href="https://www.designrush.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DesignRush</a>.</p>
