<p>â€œOptimizing for local pack rankings with precise location-based keywords and building <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/localize-google-ads">localized</a> links from directory listings and community websites is key,â€ said Lyn Collanto, marketing specialist at SEO agency <a href="https://kbaweb.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KBA Web</a>. â€œAs mobile and voice search continue to rise, enhancing on-site elements like click-to-call and direction links will also be impactful.â€</p>
