<p>â€œThese events attract potential customers and create a memorable experience associated with your brand,â€ said Randy VanderVaate, CEO of <a href="http://www.funeralfunds.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Funeral Funds of America</a>.</p>
<p>â€œBy partnering with local influencers and businesses and hosting or sponsoring local events, a company can effectively tap into the local audience,â€ Shukla said. â€œThese strategies not only enhance community engagement but also foster a sense of solidarity and support, which is particularly valuable in the current times where there&#8217;s a strong desire for community connection.â€</p>
