<p>Thatâ€™s in part because local sentiment and word-of-mouth lives online now. And so itâ€™s important to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-respond-to-google-reviews-with-examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">address both positive and negative reviews</a> instead of trying to bury the latter.</p>
