<h2>How ChatGPT will impact small business marketing</h2>
<p>For <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/03/06/how-to-use-chatgpt-for-small-business-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">small businesses in particular</a>, ChatGPT will be a welcome tool as these brands generally have more limited resources.</p>
<p>In fact, Milosz Krasinski, managing director of web consulting firm<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/chilli-fruit-web-consulting" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Chilli Fruit</a>, called it â€œa tool to help small business owners cut through the noise and stand out in a crowded digital space.â€</p>
<p>Here are some specific ways experts predict ChatGPT will impact small business marketing.</p>
<h3>Grow through automation</h3>
<p>Similar to marketing overall, ChatGPT can help small businesses automate routine tasks so they can focus on marketing, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/20/product-positioning">product development</a>, and strategic planning.</p>
<p>â€œBy using ChatGPT, SMBs can not only improve their operational efficiency but also enhance their customer experience and drive growth in their business,â€ Banioras said.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Chatgpt-impact-example-chatbot.png" alt="ChatGPT prompt asking for ChatGPT reply ideas " width="720" height="425" class="aligncenter wp-image-73001 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Chatgpt-impact-example-chatbot.png 720w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Chatgpt-impact-example-chatbot-480x283.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw" /></p>
