<p>â€œChatGPT can be particularly beneficial for small businesses as it can help them level the playing field with larger competitors by providing a high-quality customer experience at a lower cost,â€ Vij said. â€œBy using ChatGPT, small businesses can simplify many of their customer service interactions, freeing up time and resources that can be used to focus on other areas of the business.â€</p>
<h3>Learn about customers at scale</h3>
