<p>â€œTrawling through pages of information is time-consuming,â€ Mollett noted. â€œTyping in a subject, some key points and facts, and ChatGPT bringing up all the information needed is just genius.â€</p>
<p>But again, itâ€™s important to fact-check ChatGPT as the information is not going to be the most up-to-date. ChatGPT and other AI tools should be used as a starting point to build on.</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/2734.png" alt="âœ´" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Use our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Keywords_KWTool" class="waffle-rich-text-link">Free Keyword Tool </a>to find high-value keywords for your account!</div></div>
<h3>Publish content faster</h3>
