<p>Garit Boothe, CEO of <a href="https://digitalhoney.money/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Digital Honey</a>, noted this can include efforts to increase underrepresented groups, as well as to implement training and education programs and to promote diversity in leadership and decision-making roles.</p>
<p>â€œIt is also possible that there will be a greater emphasis on intersectionality and addressing the specific needs and experiences of diverse individuals,â€ he added.</p>
<p>This is something we mentioned in our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/01/03/best-marketing-strategies">Best Marketing Strategies for Small Businesses 2023</a> post.</p>
