<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/12/13/best-worst-marketing-campaigns">The 20 Best &#038; Worst Marketing Campaigns of the Year (The Small Business Version!)</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
