<h2>The best of small business<span> SMS marketing</span></h2>
<p>Just one campaign in this category, but for the better. This is a tough act to follow!</p>
<h3><span>6. The Squid Game SMS campaign</span></h3>
<p>Vitamin and supplement retailer <a href="https://www.mysupplementstore.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">My Supplement Store</a> wanted to increase its SMS subscribers before the holidays, so it created a campaign that taps into the popularity of Squid Game, which was <a href="https://www.cnet.com/news/netflix-squid-game-is-even-bigger-than-you-thought-2-billion-hours-big/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">streamed for nearly 1.7 billion hours in its first 28 days</a>. In each order placed by a customer who was not already an SMS subscriber, the brand included a business card that looked like the cards used in the Netflix show with a number to text.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/squid-game-marketing-example.png" alt="squid game marketing example" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-53604" width="448" height="453" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/squid-game-marketing-example.png 448w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/squid-game-marketing-example-297x300.png 297w" sizes="(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px" /></p>
<p>Once they texted that number, â€œthis then took them through the marble game where they could win a big discount or be eliminated,â€ said Marketing Director Brian Anderson.</p>
<p>The result was a <strong>20% increase in SMS subscribers.</strong> Anderson noted customers loved the creativity, â€œemailing us how much they enjoyed it.â€</p>
<h3>How to apply it</h3>
<p>Keep your tabs on pop culture and current trends. You never know when you&#8217;ll have an opportunity to get creative and capitalize. Also, gain inspiration from the big brands. Check out the<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/09/28/best-marketing-campaigns-examples"> five best marketing campaigns we&#8217;ve ever seen</a> (which includes tips on how to DIY) and the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/03/13/best-advertising-campaigns">same roundup for ad campaigns</a>.</p>
<h2>The best of small business social media marketing</h2>
<p>Influencer marketing, Facebook groups, and Instagram giveaways are by no means groundbreaking strategies, but take a look at the approach these businesses took that helped them win big.</p>
<h3><span>7. Influencer marketing tools</span></h3>
<p>Darshan Somashekar, CEO of game site <a href="https://im-a-puzzle.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Iâ€™m a Puzzle</strong></a>, said he uses online tools to identify potential influencers who can create user-generated content (UGC). The brand gives away products in exchange for video reviews and testimonials. It also has a collaboration program in which influencers give access to their Facebook and/or Instagram pages to advertise their content.</p>
<p>Iâ€™m a Puzzle pays these influencers $100 per month with 5% rev share for all sales generated through their links. Somashekar said the result is <strong>site traffic and social media growth</strong>.</p>
<h3>How to apply it</h3>
<p>If <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2016/08/19/influencer-marketing-content-promotion">influencer marketing</a> makes sense for your business, consider allocating enough of your budget to this channel to see a significant ROI. For example, you may want to invest in influencer marketing tools like Darshan did.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/influencer-marketing-tool-examples.png" alt="influencer finder tool example" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-53601" width="720" height="467" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/influencer-marketing-tool-examples.png 720w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/influencer-marketing-tool-examples-480x311.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw" /></p>
