<p><span lang="EN">Broadway theaters in New York are scheduled to resume performances in September 2021â€”18 months after they shuttered in the early days of the pandemic.</span></p>
<p><span lang="EN">Itâ€™s one of the clearest signs yet that a â€œnew normalâ€ is on the horizon.</span></p>
<p><span lang="EN">Indeed, with about 110 million Americans fully vaccinated as of May 2021, other pandemic-era restrictions are starting to lift on public spaces like bars, restaurants, gyms, and stadiums across the country.</span></p>
