<h3><span lang="EN">Get more out of sponsoring</span></h3>
<p><span lang="EN">â€œWe expect attendance will be up. However, sponsorship and exhibitor rates aren&#8217;t changing,â€ Neher added. â€œThis creates a golden opportunityâ€”we can reach more people for the same rates as in the past.â€</span></p>
<p><span lang="EN">Lars Skjold Iversen, search engine explorer at CMS platform<span lang="EN"> <a href="https://umbraco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Umbraco</a><span lang="EN">, agreed, noting we all have Zoom fatigue by now and will likely opt for in-person events over <a href="/blog/ws/2016/05/03/marketing-webinars">webinars</a> if given the choice. That makes live events â€œa great place for us to be.â€</span></span></span></p>
<h3><span lang="EN">Try a hybrid approach</span></h3>
