<h2>4. Keep pushing live and standard video</h2>
<p><span lang="EN">Live video is a <a href="/blog/ws/2021/01/04/best-marketing-strategies-2021">digital strategy</a> that helped brands connect with consumers from afar during the pandemicâ€”and marketers expect to continue using it after a fundamental shift in behavior during the pandemic.Â </span></p>
<p><span lang="EN">Thatâ€™s true for <span lang="EN">Derek Devore, founder of luxury real estate touring platform <a href="https://duvora.com/">Duvora</a><span lang="EN">, who said he saw a â€œmassiveâ€ uptick in adoption in 2020 as customers used live video in their searches for homes.</span></span></span></p>
<p><span lang="EN">â€œGoing forward, we are investing 90% of our efforts into live video,â€ he added. â€œThis interaction and ability to reach luxury home buyers in any part of the world instantly has proven to be the best channel for us.â€</span></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="19a82258-50ad-46bc-b946-39cb267f91b6" data-langcode="en">
