<h3>1. Optimize for Googleâ€™s next update</h3>
<p>With Googleâ€™s Page Experience Update <a href="https://searchengineland.com/the-google-page-experience-update-user-experience-to-become-a-google-ranking-factor-335252">coming in May 2021</a>, new metrics called <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/02/19/improve-core-web-vitals">Core Web Vitals</a>â€”which will measure site load time, interactivity and content stabilityâ€”will start to impact overall search rankings.</p>
