<h3>4. Focus on customer retention</h3>
<p>And for brands struggling to recover from the events of 2020, <a href="/blog/ws/2020/04/13/marketing-agencies-retention-strategies-covid-19">focusing on existing customers</a> may be wise.</p>
<p>â€œIn an <a href="/blog/ws/2020/09/24/marketing-during-recession">uncertain economy</a>, most brandsâ€”especially niche retailersâ€” shouldÂ focus on existing customers,â€ said Jonathan Frey, CMO of electric bike retailer <a href="https://urbanbikesdirect.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Urban Bikes Direct</a>.</p>
