<p>Whatâ€™s more, mobile interactions like <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/11/09/sms-marketing">SMS</a> (and even <a href="/blog/ws/2020/07/21/promotional-email-examples">email</a>) are a direct link between brand and customerâ€”and bypass third parties.</p>
