<p>Another burgeoning <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/02/22/digital-marketing-trends-2021">trend</a> with potentially far-reaching implications is <a href="/blog/ws/2020/08/13/facebook-ecommerce-tips">social commerce</a>.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="58717a92-1777-416d-b590-f89af603be9c" data-langcode="en">
