<p>Bruce Biegel, senior managing partner of management consultancy <a href="https://www.winterberrygroup.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Winterberry Group</a>, expects to see more focus on social commerce in 2021, along with new marketplaces, to <a href="/blog/ws/2015/01/26/sales-cycle">shorten the customer journey</a> from search to conversion.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="13c67c89-f979-48b4-a72b-c3dc1744ab5c" data-langcode="en">
